{"tid":778252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳中石油考慮暫停美國液化天然氣進口避關稅","createTime":"2018-08-13T14:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T14:49:17.000Z","uid":141151,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bc2a874c4cc07d8c7a478bede28b256a86ffc131","tid":778252,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"傳中石油考慮暫停美國液化天然氣進口避關稅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://invest.hket.com/article/2136441/%E5%82%B3%E4%B8%AD%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%B6%B2%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E6%B0%A3%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3%E9%81%BF%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finvest.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2136441%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%259F%25B3%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E6%259A%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B6%25B2%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2584%25B6%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%258F%25A3%25E9%2581%25BF%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A8%2585&d=3GyEJJVqm9wStTpq%2FW%2B7xDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=0bb5ddba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://invest.hket.com/article/2136441/%E5%82%B3%E4%B8%AD%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%B6%B2%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E6%B0%A3%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3%E9%81%BF%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85</a><br />\n<br />\n彭博引述消息人士報道，中石油考慮在冬季暫停進口美國液化天然氣(LNG)現貨，以避免潛在的關稅措施。 根據計劃，中石油將增加其他國家的現貨購買量，或將與東亞其他國家交換美國貨物以避免支付額外關稅。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中國本月份表示，正考慮向美國 LNG加徵25%的關稅，LNG並未包括在之前的目標商品清單中。這將直接打擊美國的天然氣出口商。冬季取暖季節時，能源需求和價格通常達到最高點，這反映中國國家主席習近平可能寧願忍受一些陣痛，也不在中美貿易爭端中讓步。<br />\n<br />\n分析員指出，若關稅在冬季之前實施，可能會增加非美國供應商在亞洲市場的競爭，從而推高今年冬季亞洲的現貨價格。澳洲、卡塔爾和東南亞最有可能受惠。</span><br />\n<br />\n中石油今年2月簽訂長達25年的協議，同意向Cheniere Energy 購買LNG，其中一部分供應料在今年開始。中國目前是美國LNG第三大買家。美國能源部副部長Dan Brouillette周三在東京接受採訪時表示，中國擬議的關稅措施可能暫時利好其他供應國，並指出他預計不會對美國能源行業造成任何重大負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n寧願捱貴氣，都絕不退讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今年低端人口會唔會又唔夠氣用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8901ad118dbdcd622602adb5bac3a7406967ca07","tid":778252,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:14:57.000Z","msg":"冬季黎到, 支那狗會否凍死1億?<br />\n<br />\n習種之陣痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac108b972671747f30fa167524cd8c5434b3d0d9","tid":778252,"uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年低端人口會唔會又唔夠氣用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n凍死1億「低端人口」, 咪可以減少大豆需求囉<br />\n<br />\n又WIN啦"},{"pid":"ff3700c768ee8cb63fbfa318cd1c720e9107acb3","tid":778252,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f11cc1bc919923b7d1baf2f34ee91be4c8bd92","tid":778252,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac108b972671747f30fa167524cd8c5434b3d0d9","tid":778252,"uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年低端人口會唔會又唔夠氣用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n凍死1億「低端人口」, 咪可以減少大豆需求囉<br />\n<br />\n又WIN啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:37:11.000Z","msg":"人均收入又堤升，GDP又升"},{"pid":"c0bf8d065adfd3a911b98351d48f1068bde94e83","tid":778252,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21521e63310a75cd8846eb2a0068589b736dae9e","tid":778252,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T17:38:28.000Z","msg":"成品油市場價格大漲（8月6日-8月13日）<br />\n<br />\n<a h